3
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:58,880
[Jinhuan]

4
00:02:58,210 --> 00:03:00,090
From now on, call me Wangtian.

5
00:03:02,710 --> 00:03:03,490
What are you laughing at?

6
00:03:04,260 --> 00:03:06,110
Why do you want to be named after a tree?

7
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:09,320
Wangtian is great.

8
00:03:09,430 --> 00:03:11,340
