9
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,260
No one can block its light.

10
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,800
This way, when you hear Wangtian in the future,

11
00:03:14,830 --> 00:03:16,070
you'll think of me.

12
00:03:16,390 --> 00:03:18,710
You'll remember the days we spent here.

13
00:03:19,370 --> 00:03:21,190
Then I'll call myself Jinhuan.

14
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,880
What's Jinhuan?

15
00:03:23,420 --> 00:03:24,510
The banded krait snake.

16
00:03:25,030 --> 00:03:26,030
It's the most venomous snake

17
00:03:26,050 --> 00:03:27,160
in this forest.

18
00:03:27,329 --> 00:03:29,050
Why do you want to be named after a snake?

19
00:03:29,870 --> 00:03:31,170
To guard the Wangtian tree.

20
00:03:31,410 --> 00:03:32,750
If anyone comes to cut down the tree,

21
00:03:32,970 --> 00:03:33,850
I'll bite them.

