36
00:05:35,780 --> 00:05:36,690
No.

37
00:05:39,060 --> 00:05:40,500
Wasn't Wang Xuehua

38
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:44,450
from the hardware store killed by you guys?

39
00:05:45,820 --> 00:05:46,940
If he's dead,

40
00:05:48,030 --> 00:05:49,950
isn't the case solved then?

41
00:05:51,180 --> 00:05:52,720
We didn't kill him.

42
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:54,330
He committed suicide.

43
00:06:09,590 --> 00:06:10,880
I still remember

44
00:06:13,430 --> 00:06:14,830
when I sent you to the police academy.

45
00:06:19,110 --> 00:06:20,500
I truly believe that was

46
00:06:20,550 --> 00:06:21,990
the wisest decision I've ever made.

47
00:06:25,300 --> 00:06:26,090
Han Qing,

48
00:06:26,950 --> 00:06:28,180
you're a good police officer.

49
00:06:29,390 --> 00:06:31,270
You'll definitely solve this case.

50
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:33,120
You know, I always have

51
00:06:33,150 --> 00:06:34,670
this image in my mind.

52
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:37,590
You're standing on that stage,

53
00:06:39,730 --> 00:06:41,350
while everyone's applauding for you.

54
00:06:42,870 --> 00:06:44,200
You've received an honor

55
