you've lost everything.

58
00:06:52,710 --> 00:06:53,790
Your father,

59
00:06:55,140 --> 00:06:55,940
your mother,

60
00:06:58,010 --> 00:06:58,970
your mentor,

61
00:07:00,510 --> 00:07:01,600
and Zhong Wei.

62
00:07:07,750 --> 00:07:09,490
If only I can trade myself

63
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:11,920
to bring them all back.

64
00:07:13,510 --> 00:07:14,400
Do you think it's possible?

65
00:07:20,590 --> 00:07:21,280
It's not.

66
00:07:22,950 --> 00:07:24,220
They can never come back.

67
00:07:35,430 --> 00:07:36,070
Xueman,

68
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,670
is there any more wine?

69
00:07:40,350 --> 00:07:41,110
I'll go get it.

70
00:08:43,090 --> 00:08:44,810
Among all the people in the world,

71
00:08:47,160 --> 00:08:48,910
only the two of us

72
00:08:49,090 --> 00:08:51,210
have the same blood flowing in our veins.

73
00:08:53,740 --> 00:08:55,660
You don't care about those honors.

74
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:01,560
You care about those who can never come back.

75
00:09:05,340 --> 00:09:06,400
Zhong Wei,

76
00:09:08,590 --> 00:09:09,580
your mentor,

77
00:09:11,250 --> 00:09:12,670
and maybe me too.

78
00:09:26,060 --> 00:09:28,510
