79
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:30,990
Do you believe that?

80
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,150
Come,

81
00:09:38,130 --> 00:09:39,300
dear sister.

82
00:09:40,820 --> 00:09:42,140
My dearest sister.

83
00:09:45,350 --> 00:09:46,150
Xueman,

84
