The day you came back,

88
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:07,050
I asked Dad to stop on the highway.

89
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:09,240
I just didn't want him to pick you up.

90
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:10,950
So, I...

91
00:10:12,230 --> 00:10:12,930
You...

92
00:10:13,170 --> 00:10:14,640
When you arrived at the hospital,

93
00:10:14,670 --> 00:10:16,870
