102
00:10:41,390 --> 00:10:42,750
It's my fault.

103
00:10:42,770 --> 00:10:44,100
it's all my fault.

104
00:10:44,130 --> 00:10:46,130
Dad, I'm sorry.

105
00:10:46,160 --> 00:10:47,840
Please wake up.

106
00:10:47,870 --> 00:10:50,760
I'll get along well with Xueman from now on.

107
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:53,190
Dad, please wake up, Dad.

108
00:10:54,060 --> 00:10:55,330
Dad.

109
00:11:03,550 --> 00:11:05,330
So many years have passed.

110
00:11:06,190 --> 00:11:08,090
We've all grown old.

111
00:11:09,550 --> 00:11:11,160
Does the truth still matter?

112
00:11:17,250 --> 00:11:18,900
It's been so many years.

113
00:11:20,140 --> 00:11:22,130
This matter has been weighing on my chest,

114
00:11:22,190 --> 00:11:23,910
